  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Under Dead</strong> is a challenging <strong>auto-shooter horde survivor roguelike</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every day it gets harder. Fight for your life!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty rises over time as you encounter not only more zombies but also new ones with special powers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/d39ec1c07ba47a98a197096ce10a67b6.poster.avif?t=1749113843\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/d39ec1c07ba47a98a197096ce10a67b6.webm?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/d39ec1c07ba47a98a197096ce10a67b6.mp4?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every run is unique</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zombies, items, weapons, abilities, and events are all randomly generated. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose from a variety of classes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All classes start with different items, but that doesn’t mean you have to stick to that playstyle for the entire game. By the end, your build might end up being completely different!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/9686a1f44e8d62c13fa69f10667d4ad0.poster.avif?t=1749113843\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/9686a1f44e8d62c13fa69f10667d4ad0.webm?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/9686a1f44e8d62c13fa69f10667d4ad0.mp4?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Under Dead</strong> is a challenging <strong>auto-shooter horde survivor roguelike</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every day it gets harder. Fight for your life!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty rises over time as you encounter not only more zombies but also new ones with special powers. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/d39ec1c07ba47a98a197096ce10a67b6.poster.avif?t=1749113843\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/d39ec1c07ba47a98a197096ce10a67b6.webm?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/d39ec1c07ba47a98a197096ce10a67b6.mp4?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Every run is unique</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zombies, items, weapons, abilities, and events are all randomly generated. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose from a variety of classes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All classes start with different items, but that doesn’t mean you have to stick to that playstyle for the entire game. By the end, your build might end up being completely different!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/9686a1f44e8d62c13fa69f10667d4ad0.poster.avif?t=1749113843\" width=620 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/9686a1f44e8d62c13fa69f10667d4ad0.webm?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2339050/extras/9686a1f44e8d62c13fa69f10667d4ad0.mp4?t=1749113843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
